@NOIR_HostAddress = http://localhost:5228
@accessToken = <paste_access_token_here>
@refreshToken = <paste_refresh_token_here>

### Health Check
GET {{NOIR_HostAddress}}/api/health
Accept: application/json

### OpenAPI Document
GET {{NOIR_HostAddress}}/api/openapi/v1.json
Accept: application/json

### API Documentation (Scalar UI)
# Open in browser: {{NOIR_HostAddress}}/api/docs

### Login (Admin)
# @name login
POST {{NOIR_HostAddress}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@noir.local",
  "password": "123qwe"
}

### Register New User
POST {{NOIR_HostAddress}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "newuser@noir.local",
  "password": "123qwe",
  "firstName": "New",
  "lastName": "User"
}

### Refresh Token
POST {{NOIR_HostAddress}}/api/auth/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "accessToken": "{{accessToken}}",
  "refreshToken": "{{refreshToken}}"
}

### Get Current User (requires auth)
GET {{NOIR_HostAddress}}/api/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

